        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"943998\">JK</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/113489-new-members/topic/help.20using.20ZMOD/near/535579081\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>unroll the definition</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>that's a bad strategy in general</p>",
